{"tid":2083581,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"牙達成為未來大馬首相人選","createTime":"2020-06-29T00:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:14:18.000Z","uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1efea6ace5cc751b5ba51983455fae7ae026858c","tid":2083581,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:17:40.000Z","msg":"大家點睇牙達？<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2020/06/27/348629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientaldaily.com.my%2Fnews%2Fnation%2F2020%2F06%2F27%2F348629&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8XwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=9a2f3276\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/nation/2020/06/27/348629</a><br />\n<br />\n敦馬宣布4黨同意沙菲益任相　安華為第一副首相<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（吉隆坡27日訊）前首相敦馬哈迪宣布，不再堅持當首相，並轉而支持沙巴民興黨主席兼沙巴首席部長拿督斯里<strong>沙菲益阿達</strong>為&ldquo;希盟+&rdquo;的首相人選。<br />\n<br />\n他說，土團黨馬派、行動黨、誠信黨、沙巴民興黨在2天前的一場非正式會議上一致同意，推選沙菲益阿達為&ldquo;希盟+&rdquo;的首相人選，並支持公正黨主席拿督斯里安華為第一副首相，土團黨署理主席慕克里茲為第二副首相。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;希盟+&rdquo;在首相人選上，從&ldquo;安慕配&rdquo;到&ldquo;馬安配&rdquo;，都一直談不攏，而在今天再取得新的突破，馬哈迪今日在发布面子書直播中透露，他與誠信黨、民興黨和行動黨領袖，6月25日在吉隆坡沙巴賓館（Rumah Tetamu Sabah）面談，並取得上述共識，即&ldquo;沙安慕&rdquo;配。"},{"pid":"9dc2068c46418a6a466bce4bb33f284c1d488ec7","tid":2083581,"uid":54653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T00:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vzxE4CZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzxE4CZ.jpg&h=0000e6a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7rZzTwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7rZzTwj.jpg&h=eeda1f24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27709b7b3f189c619d5065af400f670148644049","tid":2083581,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T01:18:04.000Z","msg":"可能cut第二家園"},{"pid":"d49f572a2b196e044394584e77e76c001cc87113","tid":2083581,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim